        "layout": true,
        "heading": "Meet our founders",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Founders.jpg",
        "details": "<b class=\"fw-500 d-block mb-2 founders-p1\">Purdy Rubin &amp; Charlotte Figg are on a mission to make natural cleaning even more effective, more effortless, and more enjoyable.</b>\n<span class=\"founders-p2\">\nFrom a Hertfordshire garage to millions of homes, their multipurpose way spray, scented with essential oils, is on the way to changing the way we feel about cleaning for good.</span>"
